object.name: SuggestedPostApprovalFailed
object.description: Describes a service message about the failed approval of a suggested post. Currently, only caused by insufficient user funds at the time of approval.
object.html_description: Describes a service message about the failed approval of a suggested post. Currently, only caused by insufficient user funds at the time of approval.
object.rst_description: Describes a service message about the failed approval of a suggested post. Currently, only caused by insufficient user funds at the time of approval.

annotations.description: Message containing the suggested post whose approval has failed. Note that the Message object in this field will not contain the reply_to_message field even if it itself is a reply.
annotations.html_description: Optional. Message containing the suggested post whose approval has failed. Note that the Message object in this field will not contain the reply_to_message field even if it itself is a reply.
annotations.rst_description: *Optional*. Message containing the suggested post whose approval has failed. Note that the :class:`aiogram.types.message.Message` object in this field will not contain the *reply_to_message* field even if it itself is a reply.
annotations.name: suggested_post_message
